Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:02.69,0:00:06.82,Main,Caster,0,0,0,,Fans of Unite Battles, \N welcome to Remota Stadium!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:06.82,0:00:11.57,Main,Caster,0,0,0,,The curtains are {\i1}moments{\i0}{ away} from lifting{lit: being cut down} on \N the special event battle you’ve all been waiting for!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:11.57,0:00:15.16,Main,Caster,0,0,0,,What kinds of twists and turns \N are in store for us?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:15.16,0:00:19.00,Main,Caster,0,0,0,,Now then, let’s get straight to the intros \N for our competing teams!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:19.00,0:00:22.17,Main,Caster,0,0,0,,Taking part will be... \N The number one center of attention!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:22.17,0:00:26.63,Main,Caster,0,0,0,,Possessing popularity and skill, \N they’re the idol team of Unite Battles! {"They've got" felt kind of plain for stadium announcer here, but most things I thought of felt too embellishy. My favorite idea was "Awash with" but argh unintentional puns. -ed}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:26.63,0:00:29.51,Main,Caster,0,0,0,,The Shining Oceans!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:29.51,0:00:31.47,Main,Caster,0,0,0,,And going up against them...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:31.47,0:00:36.18,Main,Caster,0,0,0,,Today marks their Unite Battle debut, \N but they’ve got infinite potential!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:36.18,0:00:40.48,Main,Caster,0,0,0,,A promising new team \N storms into Remota Stadium!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:40.85,0:00:43.36,Main,Caster,0,0,0,,The Rising Voltteccers!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.36,0:00:45.98,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Whoa, they’re really hyping us up! {TL: Whoa, we’re really standing out! / bleh standing out... standing out as in we're really getting spotlighted, getting shown off}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:45.98,0:00:48.15,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Give the crowd a wave, at least.{Go wave something like a hand to the customers, you hear.}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:48.15,0:00:49.57,Main,Liko Roy,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:49.57,0:00:51.36,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Awright! Just you watch!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:51.36,0:00:53.28,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Nuh-uh. No way, no way, \N no way, no way...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:54.91,0:00:58.79,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Umm... If you’re wondering \N how we ended up here...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:58.79,0:01:00.71,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,A Unite Battle?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:00.71,0:01:01.58,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,What’s that?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:01.58,0:01:05.71,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,It’s a kind of Pokémon Battle match \N using a special energy, known as Aeos Energy, {The special energy that gushes out only on the Island that's known as Aeos Island,}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:05.71,0:01:08.72,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,which gushes forth \N on an island called Aeos Island.{Aeos Energy, it's a Pokemon Battle sporting match that uses that.}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:09.26,0:01:13.14,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Teams composed of \N five trainer and Pokémon pairs...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:13.14,0:01:17.47,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,...each employ moves and strategies \N in heated battle!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:17.47,0:01:19.52,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Aeos Energy...?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:19.52,0:01:23.10,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,I think... \N you collect that Aeos Energy in battle,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:23.10,0:01:27.61,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,and use it to power up your Pokémon \N as you compete for points... or something.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:27.94,0:01:29.57,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Dot, you know about them?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:29.57,0:01:31.90,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Well... The rules, at least.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:31.90,0:01:33.87,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Okay, you’ve pretty much got it.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:34.45,0:01:37.04,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,{\q2}You see, \N I happen to know Professor Rin,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:37.04,0:01:40.87,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,{\q2}the one{person} who discovered Aeos Energy \N and created the Unite Battle system.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:41.62,0:01:46.13,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,There’s a special battle scheduled \N to be held on Aeos Island in three days,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:46.13,0:01:50.17,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,but one of the teams planning to compete \N ran into some trouble and had to drop out.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:51.05,0:01:53.80,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,Would you happen to know a team \N that could sub in for them? {You wouldn’t happen to know any other team that could substitute for them?}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:55.01,0:01:57.51,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,She asked me, so I told her...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:57.51,0:02:00.10,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,“I know the best team \N you could ever ask for!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:00.10,0:02:03.48,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,“They’re called the Rising Voltteccers!”, \N is what I said.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:03.48,0:02:04.65,Main,Kids,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:04.65,0:02:06.31,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Us?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:06.31,0:02:07.86,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Sounds fun, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:08.57,0:02:13.11,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,And so,{same phrasing as NEPs} we’re competing \N in a Unite Battle!
Comment: 0,0:02:13.74,0:02:13.74,Main,,0,0,0,,{Opening}
Comment: 0,0:03:43.83,0:03:43.83,Main,,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.84,0:03:56.38,Main,Spectator,0,0,0,,Shining! Oceans!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.76,0:03:56.38,Main,Spectator,0,0,0,,{\an8}Do your best!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.38,0:03:58.22,Main,Spectator,0,0,0,,Get another win today!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:58.22,0:03:59.97,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,That’s some serious cheering...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.97,0:04:05.22,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,The Shining Oceans are a team with \N top-class popularity {\i1}and{\i0} skill, after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.81,0:04:07.85,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,{\i1}That’s{\i0} the kind of team \N we’re up against...?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.85,0:04:11.31,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Woo! I’m so excited, \N I can’t stop shakin’!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.02,0:04:13.82,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,The battle will begin in...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.82,0:04:14.82,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,Ten...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.82,0:04:15.82,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,Nine...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.82,0:04:16.82,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,Eight...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.82,0:04:17.82,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,Seven...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.82,0:04:18.82,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,Six...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.82,0:04:19.82,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,Five...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.82,0:04:20.82,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,Four...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.82,0:04:21.82,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,Three...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.82,0:04:23.58,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,Ready...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.58,0:04:25.20,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.13,0:04:35.92,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Masquernya! Right!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.88,0:04:38.38,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Shall we go, Cap?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.38,0:04:40.51,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Loudbone, rush down the middle! {as in, the middle MOBA lane. but not overt MOBA player jargon.}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.51,0:04:42.14,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Wanival, left!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.14,0:04:43.51,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Yamirami, follow his lead!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.10,0:04:49.60,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,First, aim to power up!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.60,0:04:53.61,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Seek out wild Pokémon on the field \N and keep on challenging them to battles!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.69,0:04:58.07,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,There! Pokémon!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.07,0:05:00.57,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,They’re glowing! \N That’s Aeos Energy!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.87,0:05:04.95,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Masquernya! Acrobatics!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.25,0:05:13.96,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Dodge and use Trick Flower!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.14,0:05:31.64,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Cap! Thunder Punch!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.61,0:05:44.32,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Loudbone! Flare Song!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.63,0:05:56.59,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Yamirami! Shadow Strike!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.89,0:06:09.47,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Wanival! Air Cutter!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.61,0:06:24.61,Main,Caster,0,0,0,,They’re building up Aeos Energy \N nice and smooth!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.61,0:06:26.87,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,The energy keeps stacking up!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.87,0:06:27.99,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,This is interesting!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.99,0:06:31.75,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Don’t let your guard down. \N We’ll be closing in on the enemy.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.58,0:06:34.79,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Masquernya! Acrobatics!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.09,0:06:44.97,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Now, go for the Beequeen!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.43,0:06:49.97,Main,Negigaknight Ocean,0,0,0,,Negigaknight! Brutal Swing!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.56,0:06:55.10,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Masquernya, dodge it!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.36,0:07:05.11,Main,Caster,0,0,0,,What’s this? Pokémon from both teams \N have made contact for the first time!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.11,0:07:07.53,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Are they here to snatch the energy?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.53,0:07:11.66,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Whichever Pokémon lands the final hit \N gets the Aeos Energy.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.66,0:07:14.75,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Meaning one potential tactic \N is stealing the last hit.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.75,0:07:16.83,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,I won’t {\i1}let{\i0} them snatch it!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.83,0:07:19.25,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Masquernya! \N Use Trick Flower on Beequeen!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.80,0:07:25.97,Main,Negigaknight Ocean,0,0,0,,Guard!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.84,0:07:31.39,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Cap, support Masquernya!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.02,0:07:34.60,Main,Zoroark Ocean,0,0,0,,Zoroark! Shadow Claw!
Comment: 10,0:07:39.48,0:07:40.40,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Tsk!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.40,0:07:41.86,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Cap! Thunder Punch!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.95,0:07:52.66,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Masquernya! Acrobatics!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.79,0:08:00.79,Main,Negigaknight Ocean,0,0,0,,Not bad. But...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.42,0:08:02.67,Main,Pixie Ocean,0,0,0,,Pixie! Moonlight!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.80,0:08:12.18,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,It recovered?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.18,0:08:13.93,Main,Negigaknight Ocean,0,0,0,,Negigaknight! Consecutive Cut!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.52,0:08:19.94,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Masquernya, run for it!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.25,0:08:47.84,Main,Caster,0,0,0,,It appears the Shining Oceans \N have won the struggle for the energy!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.84,0:08:51.68,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,They got us... \N But we’re not down for the count yet!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.68,0:08:54.81,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Cap! The enemy goal is wide open! Go!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.46,0:09:25.71,Main,Caster,0,0,0,,Goal!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.71,0:09:29.72,Main,Caster,0,0,0,,In a stunning turn of events{nanto}, \N the first point goes to the Rising Voltteccers!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.84,0:09:33.97,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Nice goal there, Cap!{same phrasing as Nice guts in past eps like 044}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.97,0:09:35.35,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.35,0:09:37.10,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Awright, now me!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.10,0:09:39.52,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Go, Yamirami! Score a goal!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.52,0:09:41.02,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Hey, wait! If you just rush in—
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.02,0:09:42.52,Main,Showers Ocean,0,0,0,,Showers! Quick Turn!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.11,0:09:53.11,Main,Caster,0,0,0,,Yamirami’s down!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.49,0:09:59.29,Main,Caster,0,0,0,,It’s been sent back \N to the starting zone!{Dread Yamirami}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.79,0:10:03.54,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Gah! All that energy I gathered...!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.54,0:10:04.88,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Bad news!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.88,0:10:06.92,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,The enemies are at our goal!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.51,0:10:11.51,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Loudbone, protect the goal!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.72,0:10:15.01,Main,Zoroark Ocean,0,0,0,,They got ahead of us!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.01,0:10:16.72,Main,Strinder Ocean,0,0,0,,I’ll kick them out of the way!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.72,0:10:20.52,Main,Negigaknight Ocean,0,0,0,,No, this is {\i1}our{\i0} time to shine. \N Let’s show the stands what they’re hoping to see. {Let us respond to the hopes of the Stands.}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.52,0:10:22.52,Main,Zoroark Ocean,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.52,0:10:25.40,Main,Zoroark Ocean,0,0,0,,Zoroark! Nightfall Burst!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.95,0:10:38.45,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Wanival?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.45,0:10:41.04,Main,Strinder Ocean,0,0,0,,Strinder! Venom Distortion!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.13,0:10:56.51,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,What were those moves?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.51,0:10:57.89,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,That’s some amazing power...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.89,0:11:00.26,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,They already got powered up?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.64,0:11:04.19,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Building up Aeos Energy \N makes Pokémon power up...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.19,0:11:06.27,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,...and learn powerful new moves.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:06.27,0:11:09.15,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,They’re... Unite Moves!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.41,0:11:26.75,Main,Caster,0,0,0,,The Shining Oceans make a rush for the goal! \N They’ve turned the tables in an instant!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.75,0:11:27.88,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,They’re strong...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.88,0:11:29.79,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,They’re a top team for a reason...{sasuga. line}
Comment: 0,0:11:41.51,0:11:41.51,Main,,0,0,0,,{Part C}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.27,0:11:49.52,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,We’ve still got a chance \N to turn the tables.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.52,0:11:51.02,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,No giving up! Let’s keep at it!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.02,0:11:53.28,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,First, we need to hurry and power up.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.28,0:11:57.03,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,We need to cooperate as a team to build energy, \N rather than going in solo.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.81,0:12:31.23,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Cap, cover him!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.25,0:12:50.00,Main,Negigaknight Ocean,0,0,0,,Seems like that Pikachu’s \N their commander.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.00,0:12:52.00,Main,Negigaknight Ocean,0,0,0,,Then let’s disrupt their teamwork.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.00,0:12:53.25,Main,Negigaknight Ocean,0,0,0,,Everyone, attack him!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.25,0:12:54.13,Main,Shining Oceans,0,0,0,,{\i1}Roger!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.97,0:13:03.64,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Masquernya, use Trick Flower \N on those Runpappa!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.11,0:13:18.49,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,You powered up!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.61,0:13:21.24,Main,Pixie Ocean,0,0,0,,Pixie! Gravity!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.33,0:13:27.16,Main,Strinder Ocean,0,0,0,,Strinder! Overdrive!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:35.04,0:13:37.34,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Masquernya, support Cap!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.13,0:13:39.80,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Blooming Showtime!{Move has !! in the text in-game, though anime CCs don't include it.}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.35,0:13:49.22,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Ooh, is that a Unite Move?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.22,0:13:51.98,Main,Negigaknight Ocean,0,0,0,,Not good. \N Let’s retreat for now and regroup!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.98,0:13:56.40,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Now, Loudbone!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.98,0:13:58.98,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Go, Wanival!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.98,0:14:00.99,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Looking good, Yamirami!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:00.99,0:14:02.99,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Nice, Cap!{Similar phrasing to nice guts, nice goal}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.99,0:14:06.74,Main,Caster,0,0,0,,All the members of the Rising Voltteccers \N have powered up, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.33,0:14:10.29,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Now we can fight on an even playing field \N with their Pokémon!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.29,0:14:12.75,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,We ain’t gonna lose \N no energy struggles, neither!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.75,0:14:15.63,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,Five minutes remaining in this battle.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.04,0:14:17.59,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Only five minutes left?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.59,0:14:21.22,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Let’s use Unite Moves \N to keep up our attack and turn the tables!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.22,0:14:22.76,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,No, hold on.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:23.51,0:14:25.59,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,We’re going to \N seal off our Unite Moves.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.59,0:14:26.22,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.22,0:14:28.85,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Seal off? Like, not use them?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.85,0:14:31.77,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,But why?! \N We can’t win the battle like that!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.89,0:14:37.02,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Once you use a Unite Move, \N you can’t use it again for a while.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.02,0:14:39.82,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,And we’ve got a chance \N to {\i1}really{\i0} turn the tables coming up!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.53,0:14:43.36,Main,Showers Ocean,0,0,0,,Showers! Aquamarine Splash!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.42,0:15:03.13,Main,Zoroark Ocean,0,0,0,,The other team seems to be \N saving their Unite Moves.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.13,0:15:05.97,Main,Negigaknight Ocean,0,0,0,,Yeah. They’ve probably got \N {\i1}you-know-what{\i0} in mind. {They're likely aiming for "that".}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.64,0:15:10.89,Main,Negigaknight Ocean,0,0,0,,In which case, \N we won’t hold back on scoring plenty of goals.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:15.77,0:15:18.40,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Their lead is just growing bigger!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.40,0:15:20.90,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Can we actually turn the tables?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.28,0:15:27.53,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Hey, what was that just now?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.53,0:15:29.03,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.49,0:15:31.41,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Just what I was waiting for!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.41,0:15:33.41,Main,Caster,0,0,0,,Feast your eyes, everyone!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.41,0:15:36.42,Main,Caster,0,0,0,,As if drawn here \N by the rising Aeos Energy,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.42,0:15:44.30,Main,Caster,0,0,0,,the Legendary Pokémon Thunder... \N has just landed on the Remota Stadium Field!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:47.80,0:15:50.68,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Our chance to really \N turn the tables is Thunder?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.68,0:15:53.39,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Everyone, \N gather in the middle of the field!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.39,0:15:55.39,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Our speed against theirs! Hurry!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.39,0:15:56.19,Main,Kids,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.19,0:16:00.19,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Thunder’s Aeos Energy is far beyond...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.19,0:16:04.19,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,...that of the other wild Pokémon.{The Aeos Energy that Thunder holds can't even be compared to that of the other wild Pokemon.} \N And what’s more...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.65,0:16:08.70,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,Two minutes remaining in this battle. \N Entering the final stretch. {last spurt seems to be Final Stretch in EN game}{Provisionally going with final stretch because this is one of those annoying waseis that's so close to tracking correctly but not quite there in all cases. -ed}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.70,0:16:12.33,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,During this time, \N goals will be worth twice as many points.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.33,0:16:13.95,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Twice as many points?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.95,0:16:18.58,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,I get it... If we steal Thunder’s energy \N and make a goal, we’ll score big time!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.58,0:16:19.96,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Precisely!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.63,0:16:26.76,Main,Kids,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dodge it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.51,0:16:35.27,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Their team’s here, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.27,0:16:38.69,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,This is what’ll decide the match. \N Now, we unseal our Unite Moves!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.69,0:16:39.27,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Cap!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.27,0:16:40.90,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Full Bolt Storm!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.24,0:16:58.00,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Leave the enemy team to me! \N Go attack Thunder!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.00,0:17:01.42,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Okay! Let’s go, Loudbone! \N Rousing Symphony!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.39,0:17:20.02,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Wanival! Splashing Carnival!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.53,0:17:29.44,Main,Zoroark Ocean,0,0,0,,Zoroark! Shadow Claw!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.44,0:17:31.20,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Cap! Shadow Clones!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.71,0:17:46.55,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Their team isn’t coming \N to defeat Thunder?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.55,0:17:51.68,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,{\q2}They’ve got a big lead, so they could be prioritizing \N obstructing us over pushing for more goals.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.97,0:17:54.14,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Thunder’s up to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:54.14,0:17:55.22,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:55.22,0:17:57.10,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Yamirami, head into the grass!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.60,0:18:02.14,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Hold on! Ult?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:02.14,0:18:04.44,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,We should concentrate on Thunder!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.98,0:18:06.27,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.27,0:18:08.15,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Masquernya! Blooming Showtime!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:15.70,0:18:16.83,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,It’s working!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.83,0:18:18.58,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,{Let’s }Keep up the momentum \N and land the last hit!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.58,0:18:23.33,Main,Negigaknight Ocean,0,0,0,,Sorry, but you won’t get the chance!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.21,0:18:28.00,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Over there! Negigaknight?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.09,0:18:33.09,Main,Negigaknight Ocean,0,0,0,,Negigaknight! \N Jade Lance Flash: Negiga Nova!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.64,0:18:38.18,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Oh, no! The last hit...!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.43,0:18:41.35,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Pop out, Yamirami!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.39,0:18:46.52,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Yamirami! Chaos Gazer!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.20,0:19:02.41,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Ult! Was that... a Unite Move?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.41,0:19:05.83,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Its effect was to force a foe \N to return to their starting zone?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.83,0:19:09.59,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,So you had spotted Negigaknight... \N Incredible!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.59,0:19:11.51,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Heh! Only natural.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.51,0:19:13.22,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Hey! We don’t have time for this!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.76,0:19:15.22,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Oh right, Thunder!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.34,0:19:18.60,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Wanival! Wave Tackle!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.39,0:19:21.81,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Loudbone! Flare Song!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:22.47,0:19:25.35,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Masquernya! Trick Flower!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.86,0:19:39.03,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,All right, run for the goal!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:40.12,0:19:41.83,Main,Negigaknight Ocean,0,0,0,,Don’t let that happen! \N Stop them!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.85,0:20:03.10,Main,Kids,0,0,0,,{\i1}Go!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.23,0:20:12.65,Main,Caster,0,0,0,,The Rising Voltteccers \N score goals one after another!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.11,0:20:17.24,Main,Strinder Ocean,0,0,0,,Strinder! Overdrive!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.71,0:20:35.96,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Dunk it, Cap!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:45.85,0:20:48.39,Main,Caster,0,0,0,,And there the battle ends!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:48.39,0:20:52.02,Main,Caster,0,0,0,,The winner is... In a stunning, stunning, \N {\i1}stunning{\i0} turn of events...! {nanto, nanto, nanto}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.52,0:20:55.90,Main,Caster,0,0,0,,The Rising Voltteccers!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.16,0:21:01.70,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,We... actually won...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.70,0:21:03.03,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.03,0:21:05.49,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,What do you think? Fun, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.49,0:21:09.16,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,I got stronger yet again! \N {\i1}And{\i0} learned an awesome move!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.16,0:21:14.04,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Unite Moves can only be used in Unite Battles... \N Were you not aware?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.04,0:21:16.05,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,What?! Seriously...?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.13,0:21:18.72,Main,Negigaknight Ocean,0,0,0,,They defeated us.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.72,0:21:21.13,Main,Negigaknight Ocean,0,0,0,,Let’s train even harder \N and win next time!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.13,0:21:22.01,Main,Shining Oceans,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.98,0:21:41.40,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,{\q2}Our first Unite Battle was \N an exhilarating experience, filled with thrills!
Comment: 0,0:21:45.49,0:21:45.49,Main,,0,0,0,,{Mega-Study With Instructor Starmie A}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.62,0:21:48.20,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Friede here!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.20,0:21:51.79,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,It’s time to Mega-Study With Instructor Starmie!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.00,0:21:56.17,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Today’s topic is Strinder: High Form!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:56.17,0:22:00.05,Main,Friede,120,0,0,,{\q2}When it releases strong electricity, \N it makes a sound akin to a certain instrument echo out,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:00.05,0:22:02.22,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,but do you know what instrument that is?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:03.93,0:22:06.47,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,See the answer after the commercials!
Comment: 0,0:22:06.47,0:22:06.47,Main,,0,0,0,,{Ending}
Comment: 0,0:23:36.48,0:23:36.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{Mega-Study With Instructor Starmie B}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:39.56,0:23:41.65,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Time to announce \N the correct answer!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:41.65,0:23:43.11,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,The answer is...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:43.11,0:23:44.74,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,A: Guitar!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:45.20,0:23:50.49,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,{\q2}When you see it pluck at its chest to produce sound... \N It looks just like a rock star!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:50.49,0:23:51.83,Main,Caster,0,0,0,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:51.83,0:23:55.58,Main,Caster,0,0,0,,We’re closing out with a one-night-only \N special unit performing {\i1}on stage!{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:24:00.50,0:24:00.50,Main,,0,0,0,,{Preview}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:01.88,0:24:05.26,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Everyone! \N We’re about to arrive in Miare City!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:05.76,0:24:08.26,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,It’ll be my first time, \N so I’m really looking forward to it!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:08.26,0:24:10.97,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,There’s all sorts of Pokémon \N living in the city, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:10.97,0:24:13.60,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,I hear they’ve got \N lots of delicious food, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:14.39,0:24:17.06,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Plus, it’s your hometown, isn’t it, Ult?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:17.06,0:24:18.27,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,I s’pose!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:18.27,0:24:21.82,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,And so, to be continued \N next time on Pocket Monsters!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:21.82,0:24:24.07,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Miare City! A New Encounter
Dialogue: 10,0:24:24.07,0:24:26.24,Main,Navi,0,0,0,,Everybody, welcome!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:26.24,0:24:28.03,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Huh? Who’s that?!
