Dialogue: 3,0:22:21.49,0:22:22.74,ED,,0,0,0,,{\q2\blur0.6\pos(960,22)\c&HB8A2E5&\bord0\clip(0,72,1920,1080)}The power of hard work is amazing!
Dialogue: 3,0:22:22.74,0:22:23.24,ED,,0,0,0,,{\q2\blur0.6\pos(960,22)\c&HB8A2E5&\bord0\clip(0,72,1920,1080)}(Ahem!)
Dialogue: 3,0:22:23.24,0:22:24.74,ED,,0,0,0,,{\q2\blur0.6\pos(960,22)\c&HB8A2E5&\bord0\clip(0,72,1920,1080)}But if I slack off I might end up devolving...
Dialogue: 3,0:22:24.74,0:22:25.70,ED,,0,0,0,,{\q2\blur0.6\pos(960,22)\c&HB8A2E5&\bord0\clip(0,72,1920,1080)}Well, that’s no good!
Dialogue: 3,0:22:25.70,0:22:26.62,ED,,0,0,0,,{\q2\blur0.6\pos(960,22)\c&HB8A2E5&\bord0\clip(0,72,1920,1080)}But now you mention it...
