Dialogue: 3,0:22:29.95,0:22:32.46,ED,,0,0,0,,{\q2\blur0.6\pos(960,22)\c&HB8A2E5&\bord0\clip(0,72,1920,1080)}So stop shaking this maiden’s heart already
Dialogue: 3,0:22:32.46,0:22:33.21,ED,,0,0,0,,{\q2\blur0.6\pos(960,22)\c&HB8A2E5&\bord0\clip(0,72,1920,1080)}(Stop it!)
