Dialogue: 3,0:22:51.10,0:22:54.48,ED,,0,0,0,,{\q2\blur0.6\pos(960,22)\c&HB8A2E5&\bord0\clip(0,72,1920,1080)}Face to face with the dream I’ve always imagined...
